Context: The Consulting Project Terms are a part of the program at George Brown College, fulfilling the learning outcomes while providing real-world experience. The Consulting Work term is available during Fall, Winter, and Spring. Interested students should contact their Program Coordinator or fill out the Centre for Business Inquiry Form for enrollment details. For more information, students can contact ask.george@georgebrown.ca, call 416-415-2000 or TTY: 1-877-515-5559, and visit the Social Media Hub. The college's website information is subject to change without notice. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
